views.markdown: If you need help with "bh Cheats", you can contact Zimon, the developer, via e-mail.
Zimon is the maintainer of the package "bh Cheats". Please contact them via email for any questions on this version of the package.
If you found a mistake in the depiction or cannot download the package, you can reach out to the maintainer of the "Deniied's repo" repo, Deniied.
